show only the roll total
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Rolling one twenty sided dice.
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
    roll 1d20
\f[R]
.fi
.PP
Rolling a three four sided dices plus two.
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
    roll 3d4+2
\f[R]
.fi
.PP
Rolling a four four sided dice minus two.
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
    roll 4d4-3
\f[R]
.fi
